reviewText: This is a good show. The Double Barrel collection is a good value for what you're spending. Of course the whole series might be money better spent, but I've been given discs for gifts so i wanted to complete the set. The case is solid, the artwork is wonderful,  and the quality of the show is great.
A must have if you like Action and supense in a anime. which this has. tells a tale that is very great and keeps you watching over and over.
